    dc:description "Figure 16. Agrostis ghiesbreghtii A whole plant B ligular area C spikelet D floret, lateral view, E floret, abaxial view. Based on Gentry 9231 (MEXU). Scale bars: 3 cm (A); 1 mm (B); 1 mm (C); 0.5 mm (D, E)." ;
